{"word":"G378 - ἀναπληρόω - anaplēróō - an-ap-lay-ro'-o - Fill up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναπληρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anaplēróō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ap-lay-ro'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fill up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிறைவேற்று, நிறைவாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to fill up, make full, to supply"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G4137 - πληρόω - plēróō - play-ro'-o/4137\">G4137</a>; to <i>complete</i>; by implication to <i>occupy</i>, <i>supply</i>; figuratively to <i>accomplish</i> (by coincidence or obedience): - fill up, fulfil, occupy, supply.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1603/1603\">G1603</a>, <a href=\"#/G1604/1604\">G1604</a>, <a href=\"#/G378/378\">G378</a>, <a href=\"#/G4134/4134\">G4134</a>, <a href=\"#/G4135/4135\">G4135</a>, <a href=\"#/G4136/4136\">G4136</a>, <a href=\"#/G4137/4137\">G4137</a>, <a href=\"#/G4138/4138\">G4138</a>, <a href=\"#/G466/466\">G466</a>, <a href=\"#/G4845/4845\">G4845</a>"}]}